Sentencas: A thin Mn1.5Co1.5O4 spinel coating (1 mu m) was deposited on Crofer22APU using thermal co-evaporation technique.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the Mn1.5Co1.5O4 coating was found to be 115 s/cm at 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs

Sentencas: Subsequently, a glass ceramic sealant was deposited by slurry on the Mn1.5Co1.5O4 coating.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs

Sentencas: Thermal cycling tests were performed on Crofer22APU/Mn1.5Co1.5O4 and Crofer22APU/Mn1.5Co1.5O4/glass-ceramic samples at 800 degrees C for 500 h in air.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs

Sentencas: An excellent morphological and thermo-mechanical compatibility both of the glass ceramic sealant with Mn1.5Co1.5O4 and of the Mn1.5Co1.5O4 coating with the Crofer22APU was observed.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs

Sentencas: EDS analysis revealed the presence of Cr in the Mn1.5Co1.5O4 coating while no Cr diffusion into the glass ceramic sealant was observed after thermal cycling.
Titulo: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 protective coating on Crofer22APU produced by thermal co-evaporation for SOFCs
